{
  "stem": "27748.3",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "You we talking about Herta, who showed you by example.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Can you give me any specific example that was to influence you later on?",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, so, for instance, her example-- her husband had started out as a clerk in Germany 50 years earlier.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he ended up being head of the largest department store in Germany, through his own efforts.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He didn't come from a wealthy family.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "She did, but he hadn't.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So by the age of 35, he was head of the largest department store in Germany.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And she would tell that story over, and over, and over again.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And also, people had made big discoveries, such as Ehrlich, and so on.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And so I was tuned in to this man Paul Ehrlich.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And if you were able to see around the corner to my desk, you would see that above it, I have a little sign that says 606.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "What is all this about?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Well, Paul Ehrlich, the Nobel Prize winner, named the drug he discovered-- the first drug that was at all effective against syphilis he discovered.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "He named it Salvarsan 606.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Why 606?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, there were 605 failures.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] So, and he kept going-- you see, he must have had enormous confidence in himself that he was on to something.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And failures didn't stop him.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So that's what I'm onto.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And in many ways, that is how I've led my life in my profession, since-- that is, I operate with sort of an outsider's perspective.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "That is, if everybody else is doing it, then it's not worth doing it.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Then it's no challenge.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Just what is worth doing is the independent thing, the thing that might not be popular, that's worth doing.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So, in one sense, I'm afraid of competition.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
